description: The accu-jet® Dark Blue pro Pipette Controller, BRAND is an optimized pipette with properties of ergonomic grip, speed range dial and excellent soft blow-out control. Its ergonomic grip is compatible with different size of the hands. The speed range dial allows you to set the maximum pipette speed while still maintaining touch sensitive, continuously adjustable speed control. In addition, it has an excelllent soft blow-out control to minimize cell particle or density gradient interface interference.
name: accu-jet Dark Blue pro Pipette Controller, BRAND
